Package: blockhost-common
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-yaml
Maintainer: Blockhost Team <blockhost@example.com>
Description: Common configuration and libraries for Blockhost
 This package provides the base directory structure, configuration
 file templates, and shared Python modules used by all Blockhost
 components.
 .
 Includes:
  - /etc/blockhost/ directory structure
  - Configuration file templates (db.yaml, web3-defaults.yaml)
  - Python blockhost module with config loading and VM database
  - Root agent daemon (privileged operations via Unix socket)
